cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the use of machine learning in autonomous vehicles and focuses on safety techniques to enhance dependability and safety of machine learning algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) which deals with machine learning and its applications. The paper also discusses motion planning and perception, which are key components of robotics, hence cs.RO (Robotics) is also a likely category. The paper also discusses safety standards and engineering safety, which falls under cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses limitations and performance of machine learning algorithms, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper also discusses security limitations, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
